# API Chat Security

## Chat backend (app/api/chat/route.ts)
- Use Anthropic API only. Keep API keys server-side (env vars); never expose in client.
- Answer only from provided portfolio data (me, projects, skills). No fake claims or invented facts.
- Use zod (or equivalent) for input validation; apply basic rate limiting.
- Use strict TypeScript types for request/response; no `any` unless unavoidable.

## General
- Reusable helpers in `lib/` with clear names and typed interfaces.
- Small, single-purpose functions.
